Package: dalixos-base
Version: 0.1.2
Architecture: all
Maintainer: dalixOS Team
Homepage: figsystems.github.io/dalixOS
Depends: sudo, python3, python3-tomli-w, python3-termcolor, python3-packaging, micro, python3-pip, libc6 (>= 2.38), libcap2 (>= 1:2.10), libselinux1 (>= 3.1~)
Description: The package manager for dalixOS
 Instead of installing apps under FHS directories
 dalixOS installs them under /System/Packages and
 runs them in a bubblewrapped container. We also
 imbed bubblewrap into this because we need >= 0.11.0
